Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:46.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,片名： 斷背山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:28.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,1963年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:31.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,1963年 懷俄明州 信號山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:45.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}他媽的爛車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,You pair of deuces lookin' for work...\N{\rCHT}你倆要是來找工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I suggest you get your scrawny asses in here pronto.\N{\rCHT}趕緊拖著瘦屁股滾進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Up on Brokeback...\N{\rCHT}在斷背山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:50.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,the Forest Service has got designated campsites on the allotments.\N{\rCHT}森林管理局已劃了幾個宿營地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Them camps can be 3, 4 miles from where we pasture the woollies.\N{\rCHT}那些營地離我們放羊的地方 可有三四英里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:58.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bad predator loss if there's nobody lookin' after 'em at night.\N{\rCHT}要是沒人守夜 羊會被叼走不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:01.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, what I want is a camp tender...\N{\rCHT}所以 我要找個管營地的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:06.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,to stay in the main camp, where the Forest Service says.\N{\rCHT}按森管局的要求 待在主營區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the herder...\N{\rCHT}而放羊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,he's gonna pitch a pup tent on the QT with the sheep...\N{\rCHT}在羊群中支個小帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,and he's gonna sleep there.\N{\rCHT}並睡在那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:16.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,You eat your supper and breakfast in camp...\N{\rCHT}早晚飯可以在主營區吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,but you sleep with the sheep 100%.\N{\rCHT}但是必須得和羊睡一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,No fire, don't leave no sign.\N{\rCHT}不許生火 不許留任何痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,You roll up that tent every mornin'...\N{\rCHT}每天早上得把帳篷收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,in case Forest Service snoops around.\N{\rCHT}別讓森管局的看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah?\N{\rCHT}喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,No!\N{\rCHT}不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not on your fuckin' life.\N{\rCHT}這輩子你他媽別指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:46.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got your dogs, your .30-30, you sleep there.\N{\rCHT}帶著你的狗 還有你的30-30獵槍 睡在那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:51.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Last summer I had goddamn near 25% loss. I don't want that again.\N{\rCHT}去年夏天 我他媽的幾乎損失了1/4的羊 我再不想見到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,You.\N{\rCHT}你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fridays at noon, be down at the bridge...\N{\rCHT}每週五中午到橋那去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,with your grocery list and mules...\N{\rCHT}帶著你的食品清單和騾子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:04.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,and somebody with supplies will be there at the pick-up.\N{\rCHT}有人會開車把補給品送來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:09.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow mornin' we'll truck you up to the jump-off.\N{\rCHT}明早我們開車送你們去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jack Twist.   - Ennis.\N{\rCHT}- 傑克•崔斯特 - 埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Your folks just stop at Ennis?    - Del Mar.\N{\rCHT}- 你家人沒姓啊？ - 德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, nice to know you, Ennis Del Mar.\N{\rCHT}好 很高興認識你 埃尼斯•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,My second year up here.\N{\rCHT}我在這是第二年了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:14.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Last year, one storm, the lightnin' killed 42 sheep.\N{\rCHT}去年有場雷雨 閃電劈死了42只羊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd asphyxiate from the smell.\N{\rCHT}那臭味差點把我熏死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:23.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aguirre got all over my ass, like I was supposed to control the weather.\N{\rCHT}安奎爾罵得我狗血淋頭 好像我能呼風喚雨似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:27.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,But beats workin' for my old man. Can't please my old man, no way.\N{\rCHT}可總好過替我老子幹活 無論怎麼幹他就是不爽 沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's why I took to rodeoin'. You ever rodeo?\N{\rCHT}所以我才參加牛仔大賽 你參加過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, I mean, once in a while.\N{\rCHT}偶爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,When I got the entry fee in my pocket.\N{\rCHT}當我交得起報名費的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you from ranch people?\N{\rCHT}你是牧場出身？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was.\N{\rCHT}嗯 以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your folks run you off?\N{\rCHT}家裡趕你出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, they run themselves off. There was...\N{\rCHT}不 他們自己出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:59.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,one curve in the road in 43 miles, and they miss it.\N{\rCHT}公路上43英里的地方有個彎 他們沒拐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the bank took the ranch...\N{\rCHT}接著 銀行把牧場沒收了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,and my brother and sister, they raised me, mostly.\N{\rCHT}基本上 是哥哥姐姐把我養大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit, that's hard.\N{\rCHT}操 夠你受的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I? Thank you.\N{\rCHT}能借個火嗎？謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't let them stray.\N{\rCHT}別讓他們跑丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Joe will have your ass if you do.\N{\rCHT}不然 老闆會宰了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Only thing, don't never order soup.\N{\rCHT}還有 別訂湯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Them soup boxes are hard to pack.\N{\rCHT}湯罐子打包可不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't eat soup.\N{\rCHT}嗯 反正我不喝湯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanna watch it there. That horse has a low startle point.\N{\rCHT}小心點 那馬容易受驚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doubt there's a filly that could throw me.\N{\rCHT}恐怕還沒雌馬駒能把我扔下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's git, unless you wanna sit around tyin' knots all day.\N{\rCHT}出發吧 莫非你想在這打一天的結？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit.\N{\rCHT}媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can't wait till I get my own spread...\N{\rCHT}真想有自己的牧場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I won't have to put up with Joe Aguirre's crap no more.\N{\rCHT}就再也不用幹 喬•安奎爾這攤爛事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm savin' for a place myself.\N{\rCHT}我也在存錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:06.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alma and me, we're gonna get married when I come down off this mountain.\N{\rCHT}阿爾瑪和我 等我下山以後 我們就要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:09.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit, that stay with the sheep, no fire bullshit.\N{\rCHT}去他媽的 什麼和羊睡一起 還不許生火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:14.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aguirre got no right makin' us do somethin' against the rules.\N{\rCHT}安奎爾沒權讓我們做違規的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,No more beans.\N{\rCHT}豆子我吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn. Shit!\N{\rCHT}操 媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't know.    - Something wrong?\N{\rCHT}- 我不知道  - 有什麼不對勁的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:50.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what....\N{\rCHT}唔 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why didn't we get the powdered milk and the spuds?\N{\rCHT}為什麼沒給我們奶粉和土豆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all we got.\N{\rCHT}我們就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:56.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well....\N{\rCHT}那...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here's next week's.\N{\rCHT}這是下周的單子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:04.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Thought you didn't eat soup.    - Yeah, well, I'm sick of beans.\N{\rCHT}- 還以為你不喝湯的 - 沒錯 可我吃膩豆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Too early in the summer to be sick of beans.\N{\rCHT}夏天還長著呢 這時候就吃膩豆子可早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on.\N{\rCHT}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. Come on.\N{\rCHT}快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Whoa, whoa!\N{\rCHT}等等！嘿 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Come back here!\N{\rCHT}嘿 回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, whoa.\N{\rCHT}嘿 停 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right. Fuck it.\N{\rCHT}好啦 媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:42.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, you bastard.\N{\rCHT}好啦 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where the hell you been?\N{\rCHT}你到底去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Been up with the sheep all day, I get down here hungry as hell...\N{\rCHT}放了一天的羊 餓得眼冒金星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,and all I find is beans.\N{\rCHT}可我找到的卻只有豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,What in the hell happened, Ennis?\N{\rCHT}到底發生什麼了 埃尼斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I come on a bear is what happened.\N{\rCHT}發生什麼了？我撞上只熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goddamn horse spooked and the mules took off...\N{\rCHT}該死的馬受驚了 騾子也逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,and scattered food everywhere.\N{\rCHT}食物撒得滿地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:09.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Beans is about all we got left. Got whiskey or somethin'?\N{\rCHT}我們只剩豆子了 還有威士卡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dumb-ass mule.\N{\rCHT}蠢騾子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:25.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that. God damn.\N{\rCHT}真他媽見鬼 媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me see.\N{\rCHT}讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:39.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, we gotta do somethin' about this food situation.\N{\rCHT}得想想辦法 伙食成問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll shoot one of the sheep.\N{\rCHT}要不我打只羊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what if Aguirre finds out, huh?\N{\rCHT}好啊 要是安奎爾發現了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to guard the sheep, not eat 'em.\N{\rCHT}我們是看羊的 不是吃羊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you? There are a thousand of 'em.\N{\rCHT}你緊張什麼？那有上千隻羊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:53.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll stick with beans.\N{\rCHT}我還是吃豆子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't.\N{\rCHT}我不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\rCHT}真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gettin' tired of your dumb-ass missin'.\N{\rCHT}受夠了你的爛槍法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's get a move on.\N{\rCHT}我們得趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't want the Game and Fish to catch us with no elk.\N{\rCHT}別讓漁獵部抓住我們打麋鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. Shit.\N{\rCHT}快點 媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm commutin' four hours a day.\N{\rCHT}我一天得在路上花四小時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,I come in for breakfast, I go back to the sheep.\N{\rCHT}過來吃早飯 然後去放羊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Evenin', get 'em bedded down.\N{\rCHT}到了晚上 讓它們躺好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come in for supper, go back to the sheep.\N{\rCHT}回來吃晚飯 然後又得去看羊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Spend half the night checkin' for damn coyotes.\N{\rCHT}還得花半夜的時間防土狼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aguirre got no right to make me do this.\N{\rCHT}安奎爾沒權讓我幹這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:18.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanna switch? I wouldn't mind sleepin' out there.\N{\rCHT}要不我們換一下？ 我不介意睡那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,That ain't the point. The point is, we both ought to be in this camp.\N{\rCHT}問題不在這 問題是我們都該睡在宿營地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goddamn pup tent smells like cat piss or worse.\N{\rCHT}媽的 那小帳篷的味道比貓尿還臭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind bein' out there.\N{\rCHT}我不介意去那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm happy to switch with you...\N{\rCHT}好啊 我很樂意和你換
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:37.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I warn you, I can't cook worth a damn.\N{\rCHT}但是我得警告你 我啥都不會煮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:40.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,I am pretty good with a can opener, though.\N{\rCHT}開罐頭倒是我的強項
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:44.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't be no worse than me, then.\N{\rCHT}那你就不比我差了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here you go.\N{\rCHT}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,You won't get much sleep, I'll tell you that.\N{\rCHT}你可睡不了多久 我先告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yup. Come on.\N{\rCHT}瞭解 駕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shot a coyote up there.\N{\rCHT}在那打了只土狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:27.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a big son of a bitch. He had balls on him the size of apples.\N{\rCHT}他媽的好大一隻 睾丸能有蘋果大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:30.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,He looked like he could eat himself a camel.\N{\rCHT}看起來能吞掉一隻駱駝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want some of this hot water?\N{\rCHT}你想喝點熱水嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all yours.\N{\rCHT}都是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:07.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mmm.\N{\rCHT}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't rodeo much myself.\N{\rCHT}我很少參加牛仔大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, what's the point...\N{\rCHT}我是說 那有什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,of ridin' some piece of stock for eight seconds?\N{\rCHT}在馬背上待八秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Money's a good point.    - True enough.\N{\rCHT}- 有錢賺就行  - 那倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:33.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you don't get stomped winnin' it, huh?\N{\rCHT}要是你沒被踩死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:39.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, my old man, he was a bull rider.\N{\rCHT}我老爸是個騎牛高手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pretty well-known in his day.\N{\rCHT}曾經很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:48.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Though he kept his secrets to himself.\N{\rCHT}但他嘴嚴得很
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:53.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Never taught me a thing, never once come to see me ride.\N{\rCHT}從來沒教過我 也沒來看過我騎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your brother and sister do right by you?\N{\rCHT}你哥哥姐姐對你好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:11.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,They did the best they could after my folks was gone.\N{\rCHT}他們盡力了 畢竟我父母死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Considerin' they didn't leave us nothin'...\N{\rCHT}而且父母什麼都沒給我們留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,but $24 in a coffee can.\N{\rCHT}除了一個咖啡罐裡放的24美元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got me a year of high school.\N{\rCHT}我上了一年高中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,That was before the transmission went on the pickup.\N{\rCHT}直到貨車的變速箱壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:32.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then my sis left. She married a roughneck, moved to Casper.\N{\rCHT}然後我姐姐走了 嫁了個莽漢 搬到卡斯帕爾去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,And me and my brother...\N{\rCHT}然後我和我哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:39.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,we went and got ourselves some work on a ranch up near Worland.\N{\rCHT}我們去沃蘭德附近一個農場打工
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Till I was 19. Then he got married.\N{\rCHT}直到我19歲 然後他也結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,And no more room for me.\N{\rCHT}然後就沒我待的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:54.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's how come me end up here.\N{\rCHT}所以我才到這兒來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:11.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Man, that's more words than you've spoke in the past two weeks.\N{\rCHT}老兄 這比你過去兩周說的話都多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:14.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hell, that's the most I've spoke in a year.\N{\rCHT}哼 我一年都沒說過這麼多話了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:23.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,But my dad, he was a fine roper.\N{\rCHT}而我老爸 是個套圈高手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:25.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Didn't rodeo much, though.\N{\rCHT}但很少參加牛仔大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:28.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,He thought rodeo cowboys was all fuck-ups.\N{\rCHT}他覺得那些牛仔 都沒什麼出息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:32.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,The hell they are.\N{\rCHT}這可沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:35.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well....\N{\rCHT}好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:42.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,There you go.\N{\rCHT}又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:48.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm spurrin' his guts out! Wavin' to the girls in the stands!\N{\rCHT}我用馬刺踢得它亂蹦亂跳 對看臺的姑娘們招手微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:51.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's kickin' me to high heaven, but he don't jackboard me! No!\N{\rCHT}它把我扔上天空 但它別想把我甩下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:58.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think my dad was right.\N{\rCHT}我想我爸是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:45.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tent don't look right.\N{\rCHT}帳篷看起來不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:48.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it ain't goin' nowhere. Let it be.\N{\rCHT}反正它也去不了哪 隨它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:53.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,That harmonica don't sound quite right either.\N{\rCHT}你那口琴吹得也不怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:56.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause it got kind of flattened when that mare threw me.\N{\rCHT}那母馬把我甩下來的時候 口琴摔走調了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, yeah?    - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 哦 是嗎？ - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:01.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought you said that mare couldn't throw you.\N{\rCHT}我還以為你說過那母馬拿你沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.93,0:24:03.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,She got lucky.\N{\rCHT}它走運罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:08.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, if I got lucky, that harmonica would've broke in two.\N{\rCHT}是嘛 要是我走運 那口琴大概就成兩瓣了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:16.11,chs,,0,0,0,,\N{\fn華文楷體}我知道審判日時我會見到你\N{\fs16\fnCronos Pro Subhead}∮ I know I shall meet you on that final day ∮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:22.28,chs,,0,0,0,,\N{\fn華文楷體}踏水無痕的基督啊 請帶我離開\N{\fs16\fnCronos Pro Subhead}∮ Water-walking Jesus, take me away! ∮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.36,0:24:25.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Very good.    - Oh, yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 唱得不錯  - 哦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:29.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,My mama, she believes in the Pentecost.\N{\rCHT}我媽媽 她相信聖靈降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.36,0:24:30.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?\N{\rCHT}哦 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:34.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,What exactly is the Pentecost?\N{\rCHT}聖靈降臨到底是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.83,0:24:37.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, my folks, they was Methodist.\N{\rCHT}我父母 他們都是衛理公會派的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:40.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Pentecost.\N{\rCHT}聖靈降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:43.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I don't know what the Pentecost is.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 我不知道聖靈降臨是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.41,0:24:47.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mom never explained it to me. I guess it's when the world ends...\N{\rCHT}媽媽從來沒對我解釋過 我猜大概是世界末日的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:51.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,and fellas like you and me, we march off to hell.\N{\rCHT}像你和我這樣的傢伙 出發去地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:24:53.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Speak for yourself.\N{\rCHT}別扯上我 好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:24:57.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,You may be a sinner, but I ain't yet had the opportunity.\N{\rCHT}你可能是有罪的 可還沒輪到我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.09,0:25:01.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.30,0:25:06.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit!\N{\rCHT}媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.13,0:25:10.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go up to the sheep now.\N{\rCHT}我去看羊了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.10,0:25:11.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give 'em hell.\N{\rCHT}操它媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.71,0:25:19.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, I'm....\N{\rCHT}不 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.38,0:25:24.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can hardly stand. It's too late to go to them sheep.\N{\rCHT}你站都站不穩 現在去羊那兒也晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.69,0:25:30.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, you got an extra blanket?\N{\rCHT}你還有多餘的毯子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.82,0:25:34.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll just roll up out here, grab 40 winks...\N{\rCHT}我就待在這 打幾個盹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.06,0:25:37.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'll ride out at first light.\N{\rCHT}天一亮就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.50,0:25:44.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll freeze your ass off when that fire dies down.\N{\rCHT}等火熄了 把你凍死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.27,0:25:45.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's good.\N{\rCHT}哦 這毯子不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.64,0:25:47.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're better off sleepin' in the tent.\N{\rCHT}最好來帳篷裡睡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.67,0:25:48.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.44,0:25:51.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.18,0:26:30.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Ennis!    - What?\N{\rCHT}- 埃尼斯  - 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.15,0:26:33.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just quit your yammerin' and get in here!\N{\rCHT}別在那哼哼唧唧的了 趕快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.21,0:27:37.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.\N{\rCHT}來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.59,0:27:48.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doin'?\N{\rCHT}你要幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.32,0:29:57.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,See you for supper.\N{\rCHT}晚飯見
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:29:59.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Come on.\N{\rCHT}駕
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:39.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on.\N{\rCHT}駕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.15,0:32:06.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a one-shot thing we got goin' on here.\N{\rCHT}那是一時衝動 就當沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.36,0:32:14.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's nobody's business but ours.\N{\rCHT}那不關其他人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.36,0:32:18.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know I ain't queer.\N{\rCHT}你知道我不是玻璃（同性戀的蔑稱）
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.33,0:32:20.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Me, neither.\N{\rCHT}我也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.54,0:33:36.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.04,0:33:39.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\N{\rCHT}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.78,0:33:43.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\N{\rCHT}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.35,0:33:45.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lie back. Come on.\N{\rCHT}躺回來 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.58,0:34:49.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Twist.\N{\rCHT}崔斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.38,0:34:53.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your Uncle Harold's in the hospital with pneumonia.\N{\rCHT}你叔叔哈樂德得了肺炎住醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.22,0:34:55.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Docs don't expect he'll make it.\N{\rCHT}醫生估計他撐不過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.46,0:34:59.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your ma sent me to tell you, so here I am.\N{\rCHT}你媽媽讓我來告訴你 所以我就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.69,0:35:03.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bad news.\N{\rCHT}真是壞消息
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.80,0:35:08.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,There ain't nothin' I can do about it up here, I guess.\N{\rCHT}可我在這兒也幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.53,0:35:12.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's not much you can do about it down there, neither.\N{\rCHT}你去了那兒也幫不了什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.87,0:35:17.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not unless you can cure pneumonia.\N{\rCHT}除非你會治肺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.38,0:35:52.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,God damn! Jesus!\N{\rCHT}媽的 天啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.71,0:35:55.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Them sheep will drift if I don't get back up there tonight!\N{\rCHT}要是我今晚不回去的話 那群羊會跑丟的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.65,0:35:58.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll get pitched off your mount in a storm like this.\N{\rCHT}這麼大的冰雹 能把你從馬上砸下來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.72,0:36:01.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll wish you hadn't tried it!\N{\rCHT}聽我的 別去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.79,0:36:03.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's too cold! Close it up!\N{\rCHT}太冷了 關上
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.50,0:36:16.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do now, huh?\N{\rCHT}我們現在怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.17,0:36:20.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get on in there and untangle 'em Chilean sheep out of ours, I guess.\N{\rCHT}過去把那群智利羊和咱們的分開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.27,0:36:23.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, where is it? Shit!\N{\rCHT}在他媽的哪呢？操
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.18,0:36:31.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,God, half the goddamn paint brands have wore off!\N{\rCHT}一半羊身上 那該死的油印已經褪了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.32,0:36:36.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,We gotta try. The least we can do is get the count right for Aguirre.\N{\rCHT}我們得試試 至少得把數目給安奎爾湊齊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.62,0:36:39.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Fuck Aguirre!    - Oh, yeah, fuck Aguirre.\N{\rCHT}- 操他媽的安奎爾！ - 沒錯 操他媽的安奎爾
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.56,0:36:42.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,What if we need to work for him again? You think of that?\N{\rCHT}可我們還是需要替他幹活 你想過沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.49,0:36:44.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,We gotta stick this out, Jack.\N{\rCHT}我們得堅持到底 傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.58,0:37:04.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll run them sheep off again if you don't quiet down.\N{\rCHT}再不安靜一會 羊都得讓你嚇跑
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.59,0:37:42.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.59,0:37:45.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aguirre came by again.\N{\rCHT}安奎爾又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.96,0:37:48.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Says my uncle didn't die after all.\N{\rCHT}說我叔叔最後挺過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.13,0:37:50.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Says bring 'em down.\N{\rCHT}還說把羊趕下山
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.90,0:37:53.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bring 'em down, why? It's the middle of August.\N{\rCHT}下山？為什麼？這才是八月中旬
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.27,0:37:57.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Says there's a storm comin', movin' in from the Pacific.\N{\rCHT}他說又有場暴風雪從太平洋那兒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.50,0:37:59.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Worse than this one.\N{\rCHT}比這場還猛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.97,0:38:03.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,That snow barely stuck an hour. Huh?\N{\rCHT}那雪下了都沒一個小時 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.04,0:38:08.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Besides, that son of a bitch, he's cuttin' us out a whole month's pay.\N{\rCHT}而且 那婊子養的肯定要扣我們一個月工錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.98,0:38:10.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,lt ain't right.\N{\rCHT}沒這個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.58,0:38:13.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well...\N{\rCHT}那...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.19,0:38:16.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can spare you a loan, bud, if you're short on cash.\N{\rCHT}我能借你點 老兄 如果你缺錢花
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.86,0:38:18.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give it to you when we get to Signal.\N{\rCHT}等我們到信號鎮就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.79,0:38:20.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't need your money, huh?\N{\rCHT}我又不需要你的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.16,0:38:24.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, I ain't in the poorhouse. Shit!\N{\rCHT}我他媽又不是窮光蛋 媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.03,0:38:27.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.47,0:39:02.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Time to get goin', cowboy.\N{\rCHT}該上路了 牛仔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.95,0:39:19.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here! This ain't no rodeo, cowboy!\N{\rCHT}過來 這可不是表演 牛仔！
