Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.38,0:58:15.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here, come here.\N{\rCHT}來啦 來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.85,0:58:18.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hi, Monroe.    - Hey, Ennis.\N{\rCHT}- 嗨 門羅 - 嗨 埃尼斯
