Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.00,0:58:27.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse us! Yeah, excuse me.\N{\rCHT}勞駕 勞駕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.56,0:58:30.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, honey. Honey, what are y'all doing here?\N{\rCHT}嘿 親愛的 你們怎麼都來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.57,0:58:31.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Big hurry.\N{\rCHT}有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.70,0:58:34.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,My boss called and, well, he wants me to go up to the ranch.\N{\rCHT}我老闆打電話來 要我去牧場
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.71,0:58:35.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mama.\N{\rCHT}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.77,0:58:37.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I guess all the heifers must've decided...\N{\rCHT}我估計所有的小母牛打算
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.44,0:58:38.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,to calve at the same time.\N{\rCHT}一起生小牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.04,0:58:41.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,I figured I could drop the girls off with you.\N{\rCHT}我覺得我只能把孩子留給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.08,0:58:42.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis, well...\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯 可是...
