Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.96,0:58:55.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alma, I can't afford not to be there when the heifers calve.\N{\rCHT}阿爾瑪 生小牛的時候我不能不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.79,0:58:57.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, it'd be my job if I lose any of 'em.\N{\rCHT}不然我肯定要沒工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.83,0:58:59.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,What about my job?\N{\rCHT}那我的工作怎麼辦？
