Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.02,0:59:21.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.\N{\rCHT}哦 天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.99,0:59:23.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Okay.    - Monroe, I'm so sorry.\N{\rCHT}- 沒事  - 門羅 我真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.85,0:59:25.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's okay, Alma.\N{\rCHT}沒事 沒事 阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.22,0:59:28.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll clean this up just as soon as I call my sister...\N{\rCHT}等我打完電話讓我姐姐帶孩子以後
