Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.86,0:59:32.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Really, Alma, it's okay. I'll get it.\N{\rCHT}真的 阿爾瑪 沒事 我來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.33,0:59:34.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Alma, come with me.    - Watch your feet.\N{\rCHT}- 阿爾瑪 跟我來  - 小心腳下啊
