Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.12,1:03:21.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch.\N{\rCHT}婊子養的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.50,1:03:28.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here.\N{\rCHT}過來
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.33,1:04:32.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alma, this is Jack Twist.\N{\rCHT}阿爾瑪 這就是傑克•崔斯特
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.23,1:04:34.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,And, Jack, this is my wife, Alma.\N{\rCHT}傑克 這是我妻子 阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.73,1:04:36.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Howdy.    - Hello.\N{\rCHT}- 你好啊  - 你好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.44,1:04:39.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got a kid.\N{\rCHT}你有孩子了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.67,1:04:42.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got two little girls. Alma Jr. and Jenny.\N{\rCHT}嗯 兩個女兒 小阿爾瑪和珍妮
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.24,1:04:44.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I got a boy.     - Yeah?\N{\rCHT}- 我有個兒子  - 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.58,1:04:48.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eight months old. Smiles a lot.\N{\rCHT}八個月大了 總是笑
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.58,1:04:51.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,I married the prettiest little gal in Childress, Texas.\N{\rCHT}我娶了德州奇德瑞斯最漂亮的妞
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.88,1:04:53.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah?     - Lureen.\N{\rCHT}- 是嗎？  - 洛琳
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.22,1:04:59.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,So me and Jack, we're gonna head out and get ourselves a drink. Yeah?\N{\rCHT}我和傑克出去喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.69,1:05:03.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sure enough.     - Pleased to meet you, ma'am.\N{\rCHT}- 當然  - 很高興見到你 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.59,1:05:04.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,We might not get back tonight...\N{\rCHT}我們今晚可能不回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.00,1:05:07.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,when we get to drinkin' and talkin' and all.\N{\rCHT}我們可能整夜喝酒聊天啥的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.26,1:05:08.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis?\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.33,1:05:10.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you get me a pack of smokes?\N{\rCHT}你能給我帶包煙回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.87,1:05:13.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you need smokes, Alma, they're in the top pocket of my blue shirt.\N{\rCHT}我藍襯衫上面口袋裡就有煙
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.84,1:05:15.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,There in the bedroom.\N{\rCHT}就在臥室裡
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.84,1:05:21.46,chs,,0,0,0,,\N{\fn華文楷體}汽車旅館
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.08,1:05:30.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Four years. Damn!    - Yeah, four years.\N{\rCHT}- 四年了 媽的  - 是啊 四年了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.82,1:05:36.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Didn't think I'd hear from you again.\N{\rCHT}沒想到還會收到你的信
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.93,1:05:39.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I figured you were sore from that punch.\N{\rCHT}我以為那拳把你打疼了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.46,1:05:43.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right next summer, I drove back up to Brokeback.\N{\rCHT}第二年夏天我還開車去過斷背山
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.50,1:05:45.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Talked to Aguirre about a job, and....\N{\rCHT}問安奎爾找工作
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.70,1:05:48.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,He told me you hadn't been back, so I left.\N{\rCHT}他說你沒回來 於是我走了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.93,1:05:51.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Went down to Texas for rodeoin'.\N{\rCHT}去德州參加牛仔大賽
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.94,1:05:54.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's how I met Lureen.\N{\rCHT}在那認識了洛琳
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.77,1:05:58.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Made $2,000 that year, bull ridin'. Nearly starved.\N{\rCHT}一整年騎在牛背上 只掙兩千塊 飯都吃不飽
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.98,1:06:04.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lureen's old man makes serious money, farm machine business.\N{\rCHT}洛琳老爸掙大錢的 做農機生意
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.45,1:06:06.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course, he hates my guts.\N{\rCHT}當然 他討厭我參加比賽
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:14.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And the Army didn't get you?    - No, too busted up.\N{\rCHT}- 軍隊沒收你？ - 沒 很失敗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.33,1:06:16.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,And rodeoin' ain't what it was in my daddy's day.\N{\rCHT}競技牛仔也遠不及我老子那時候風光了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.70,1:06:19.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got out while I could still walk.\N{\rCHT}趁我沒折了腰 去幹別的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.20,1:06:25.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Swear to God, I didn't know we was goin' to get into this again.\N{\rCHT}對天發誓 真沒想到 我們還能像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.91,1:06:29.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes I did. I red-lined it all the way.\N{\rCHT}真的 我可是一路飛奔過來的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.98,1:06:32.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get here fast enough.\N{\rCHT}生怕耽擱了一會兒
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.68,1:06:36.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What about you?    - Me? I don't know.\N{\rCHT}- 你呢？ - 我？我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.09,1:06:41.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\N{\rCHT}說不上來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.06,1:06:49.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Old Brokeback got us good, don't it?\N{\rCHT}在斷背山上我們過得很好 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.07,1:06:57.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do now?\N{\rCHT}現在怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.07,1:07:03.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,I doubt there's nothin' we can do.\N{\rCHT}恐怕沒得選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.01,1:07:10.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,So now I'm stuck with what I got here.\N{\rCHT}所以我只能照舊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.95,1:07:18.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Makin' a livin' is about all I got time for now.\N{\rCHT}眼下 謀生便是我全部生活
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.08,1:07:43.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey.\N{\rCHT}嗨
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.45,1:07:46.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, me and Jack is headed up the mountain for a day or two.\N{\rCHT}我和傑克要去山上待幾天
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.32,1:07:48.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do ourselves a little fishin'.\N{\rCHT}去釣魚
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.73,1:07:59.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, your friend could come inside, have a cup of coffee.\N{\rCHT}讓你朋友進屋坐坐 喝杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.43,1:08:01.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, he's from Texas.\N{\rCHT}他是德州人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.10,1:08:04.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Texans don't drink coffee?\N{\rCHT}德州人不喝咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.75,1:08:15.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You sure that foreman won't fire you for takin' off?\N{\rCHT}你確信工頭不會因為翹班而開除你？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.98,1:08:17.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, that foreman, he owes me.\N{\rCHT}那工頭欠我人情
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.98,1:08:21.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I worked through a blizzard last Christmas. You remember that?\N{\rCHT}去年聖誕的活 多大的風雪 還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.12,1:08:24.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'll only be a couple of days.\N{\rCHT}再者 我只去幾日罷了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.16,1:08:30.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bring fish, Daddy. A big, big one!\N{\rCHT}帶魚回來 爸爸 大大的大魚！
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.44,1:08:39.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here. Come here.\N{\rCHT}來 來
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.28,1:08:46.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here.\N{\rCHT}來
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.85,1:08:51.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,See you Sunday, latest.\N{\rCHT}周日見 最晚
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.19,1:09:04.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm starvin'. Want to get somethin' to eat?\N{\rCHT}我餓死了 來點吃的？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.13,1:09:05.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yup.\N{\rCHT}好
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.46,1:09:34.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Last one in!\N{\rCHT}看誰先！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.71,1:09:56.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is there anything interestin' up there in heaven?\N{\rCHT}天上有什麼好看的？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.12,1:09:59.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I was just sending up a prayer of thanks.\N{\rCHT}我剛剛禱告上天感激它
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.52,1:10:01.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,For what?\N{\rCHT}感激什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.66,1:10:06.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,For you forgettin' to bring that harmonica.\N{\rCHT}感激你總算忘了帶口琴來
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.49,1:10:08.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm enjoying the peace and quiet.\N{\rCHT}我喜歡平靜和安寧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.13,1:10:16.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know it could be like this, just like this, always.\N{\rCHT}其實可以就這樣的 你和我 永遠
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.50,1:10:19.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah? How do you figure that?\N{\rCHT}是嗎？你怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.44,1:10:26.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,What if you and me had a little ranch somewhere...\N{\rCHT}你和我找個小農莊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.18,1:10:31.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,a little cow-and-calf operation? It'd be a sweet life.\N{\rCHT}幹些牛犢的生意 你覺得呢？會是很好的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.85,1:10:33.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, hell, Lureen's old man...\N{\rCHT}我是說 該死的 洛琳她老子...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.85,1:10:35.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,you bet he'd give me a down payment to get lost.\N{\rCHT}肯定巴不得我早點滾蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.02,1:10:38.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, he more or less already said it.\N{\rCHT}或多或少 他早就把話講明瞭
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.06,1:10:41.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, l...\N{\rCHT}不 我...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.30,1:10:46.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told you it ain't gonna be that way.\N{\rCHT}我告訴過你的 那樣是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.30,1:10:50.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know...\N{\rCHT}知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.50,1:10:54.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,you got your wife and baby in Texas.\N{\rCHT}在德州你有妻兒
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.84,1:10:58.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, I got my life in Riverton.\N{\rCHT}而我 在瑞弗頓也有老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.14,1:11:00.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\N{\rCHT}就這些？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.75,1:11:04.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You and Alma, that's a life?      - Now you shut up about Alma.\N{\rCHT}- 你和阿爾瑪 那也算過日子？ - 閉嘴 別提阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.75,1:11:06.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,This ain't her fault.\N{\rCHT}這不是她的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.82,1:11:10.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,The bottom line is...\N{\rCHT}最起碼...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.79,1:11:13.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,we're around each other...\N{\rCHT}我們還能見見面...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.19,1:11:16.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,and this thing grabs hold of us again...\N{\rCHT}萬一我們的事 在錯誤的時間
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.80,1:11:19.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the wrong place...\N{\rCHT}錯誤的地點
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.40,1:11:22.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the wrong time...\N{\rCHT}讓別人知道
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.83,1:11:24.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we're dead.\N{\rCHT}我們就死定了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.81,1:11:28.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I tell you...\N{\rCHT}告訴你...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.34,1:11:32.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,there were these two old guys ranched up together down home.\N{\rCHT}在我家鄉 曾有兩個傢伙 一起經營農場
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.21,1:11:35.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Earl and Rich.\N{\rCHT}叫厄爾和裡奇
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.45,1:11:38.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they was a joke in town...\N{\rCHT}他們是鎮上的笑料
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.98,1:11:41.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,even though they were pretty tough oId birds.\N{\rCHT}即便他倆都是挺狠的角色
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.13,1:11:49.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anyway, they found EarI dead...\N{\rCHT}總之 後來他們在一處灌渠裡
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.00,1:11:52.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,in an irrigation ditch.\N{\rCHT}發現厄爾的屍體
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.50,1:11:57.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,They took a tire iron to him, spurred him up...\N{\rCHT}身上掛著輪胎圈 被插上馬刺
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.57,1:12:00.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,and drug him around by his dick till it pulled off.\N{\rCHT}有人拽著他的老二 直到硬生生扯下來
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.64,1:12:07.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You seen this?     - Yeah, I was what? Nine years old.\N{\rCHT}- 你去看了？ - 嗯 那時我9歲
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.48,1:12:12.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,My daddy, he made sure me and my brother seen it.\N{\rCHT}我爸一定要我和我哥去看
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.16,1:12:19.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hell, for all I know, he done the job.\N{\rCHT}該死的 我想 就是他幹得
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.26,1:12:25.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two guys living together? No way.\N{\rCHT}兩個男人一起生活？門都沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.80,1:12:30.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, we can get together once in a while...\N{\rCHT}現在 我們可以偶爾見見面
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.14,1:12:33.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,way the hell out in the middle of nowhere, but....\N{\rCHT}他媽的找個偏僻沒人的地方 可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.07,1:12:35.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Once in a while."\N{\rCHT}"偶爾"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.04,1:12:39.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Every four fucking years?\N{\rCHT}每他媽隔4年？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.38,1:12:43.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can't fix it, Jack, you gotta stand it.\N{\rCHT}既然無力去改變 傑克 那麼只能去忍受
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.79,1:12:48.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,For how long?\N{\rCHT}忍多久？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.59,1:12:52.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,As long as we can ride it.\N{\rCHT}能忍則忍
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.73,1:13:00.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,There ain't no reins on this one.\N{\rCHT}這可不能感情用事
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.68,1:13:17.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's nearly suppertime.\N{\rCHT}快到晚飯時間了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.88,1:13:18.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where the hell do you think you're going?\N{\rCHT}你要去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.02,1:13:20.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,To work!\N{\rCHT}去上班！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.19,1:13:22.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I thought you had the day off!     - Well, you thought wrong!\N{\rCHT}- 我想你不是休假嗎！ - 那你想錯了！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.65,1:13:25.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The girls need to be fed.     - Well, you take care of it!\N{\rCHT}- 孩子需要照料  - 那你去照料！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.12,1:13:27.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alma! Alma!\N{\rCHT}阿爾瑪！阿爾瑪！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.13,1:13:29.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Supper's on the stove!\N{\rCHT}菜還在爐子上！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.56,1:13:31.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,No one's eatin' unless you're servin' it!\N{\rCHT}你不張羅上菜 我們怎麼吃飯？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.60,1:13:33.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I already promised I'd take the extra shift!\N{\rCHT}我答應了要加班的！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.83,1:13:36.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fucking tell 'em you made a mistake, then!\N{\rCHT}他媽的告訴他們你錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.40,1:13:38.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,God damn it, Alma! Alma!\N{\rCHT}該死的 阿爾瑪！阿爾瑪！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.95,1:13:50.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,You girls need a push or somethin'?\N{\rCHT}要我推一把嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.82,1:13:51.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.16,1:14:03.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen to her purr, gentlemen!\N{\rCHT}聽聽這聲響 先生們！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.23,1:14:05.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,You ain't gonna get that with your Caddy!\N{\rCHT}你們的卡迪拉克可沒這動靜哦！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.76,1:14:08.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told you what she could do, and now let me show you.\N{\rCHT}耳聽為虛 眼見為實
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.40,1:14:14.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Say, didn't that pissant used to ride the bulls?\N{\rCHT}瞧 那膽小鬼以前是不是當過競技牛仔的？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.18,1:14:18.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,He used to try.\N{\rCHT}小打小鬧而已
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.58,1:14:54.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Honey, have you seen my blue parka?\N{\rCHT}親愛的 看見我的藍大衣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.21,1:14:56.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Last time I seen it, you was in it...\N{\rCHT}上回見你穿
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.85,1:14:59.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,day we had that big ice storm.\N{\rCHT}還是那次暴風雪的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.32,1:15:02.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, could have sworn I seen it in here.\N{\rCHT}怪了 明明見著是在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.49,1:15:05.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know...\N{\rCHT}我說...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.83,1:15:08.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,you've been going up to Wyoming all these years.\N{\rCHT}這些年你常去懷俄明
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.99,1:15:11.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why can't your buddy come down here to Texas and fish?\N{\rCHT}為什麼你夥伴不來德州釣魚？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.90,1:15:14.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because the Bighorn Mountains ain't in Texas.\N{\rCHT}因為德州沒有大山
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.67,1:15:17.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I don't think that his pickup could make it down here, anyway.\N{\rCHT}並且我想他的小破車也開不到這來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.74,1:15:20.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,New model comin' in this week, remember?\N{\rCHT}新型號這周就來了 記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.04,1:15:23.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're the best combine salesman we got.\N{\rCHT}你是我們最好的收割機推銷員
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.51,1:15:26.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're the only combine salesman, in fact.\N{\rCHT}實際上 你是唯一的推銷員
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.28,1:15:29.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be back in a week. That is, unless I freeze to death...\N{\rCHT}行 我一周後就回來 除非我凍死
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.28,1:15:30.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'll freeze if I don't find that parka.\N{\rCHT}要是找不到大衣 我真的要凍死了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.98,1:15:33.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't have your goddamn parka.\N{\rCHT}我可沒拿你那該死的大衣
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.19,1:15:36.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, you're worse than Bobby when it comes to losin' stuff.\N{\rCHT}丟三落四的 你比波比還嚴重
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.12,1:15:38.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, speakin' of Bobby, did you call his school...\N{\rCHT}提起波比 你給學校打電話了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.22,1:15:40.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,about gettin' him a tutor?\N{\rCHT}給他找個家庭教師
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.86,1:15:42.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought you were gonna call.\N{\rCHT}我以為你會打
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.23,1:15:44.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I complain too much. That teacher don't like me. Right.\N{\rCHT}我抱怨太多 老師不喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.93,1:15:48.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Now it's your turn.     - Okay, fine, so I'll call later.\N{\rCHT}- 該你了  - 那好 回頭我去打
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.17,1:15:52.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right. Fine.\N{\rCHT}那好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.77,1:15:54.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.\N{\rCHT}再見
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.84,1:15:58.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got 14 hours of driving ahead of me.\N{\rCHT}還要開14小時的車
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.14,1:16:00.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,See now, it don't seem fair...\N{\rCHT}你瞧 這就不公平了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.08,1:16:02.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,you goin' up there two, three times a year...\N{\rCHT}每年你去兩三趟
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.15,1:16:04.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,with him never comin' down here.\N{\rCHT}而他卻從不來這
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.10,1:16:23.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis, they got an opening over at the power company.\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯 電廠有個工作機會
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.54,1:16:25.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Might be good pay.\N{\rCHT}可能薪水好些
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.14,1:16:28.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, as clumsy as I am, I'd probably get electrocuted.\N{\rCHT}我笨手笨腳的 可能會被電死
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.41,1:16:30.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy, the church picnic's next weekend.\N{\rCHT}爸爸 下周教會野餐
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.91,1:16:33.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Will you be back from fishing by next weekend?\N{\rCHT}下周你會回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.08,1:16:34.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please, Daddy? Please!\N{\rCHT}求你啦 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.98,1:16:37.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, all right, as long as I don't have to sing.\N{\rCHT}那好 只要別讓我唱歌便是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.92,1:16:40.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.79,1:16:42.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,You forgettin' somethin'?\N{\rCHT}忘了什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.59,1:17:21.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're late.\N{\rCHT}你遲到了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.33,1:17:23.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look what I brought.\N{\rCHT}瞧我帶了什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.30,1:17:26.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,This way.\N{\rCHT}這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.85,1:17:45.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,There you go! No hands!\N{\rCHT}你來吧！我撤手
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.45,1:17:48.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all yours, buddy! It's all yours.\N{\rCHT}你來開 你來開
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.16,1:17:54.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.\N{\rCHT}來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.34,1:18:06.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on in, AIvin.\N{\rCHT}進來 艾爾文
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.24,1:18:09.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to call you for hours.\N{\rCHT}我一直在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.67,1:18:12.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Saturday night, you know, we could still smarten up...\N{\rCHT}週六晚上了 我們還可以穿戴一下
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.24,1:18:14.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,and head on over to the church social.\N{\rCHT}去參加教會活動
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.51,1:18:17.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,That fire and brimstone crowd?\N{\rCHT}那無聊難纏的活動？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.02,1:18:22.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be nice.\N{\rCHT}我覺得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.94,1:18:39.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis.\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.37,1:18:41.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,As far behind as we are on the bills...\N{\rCHT}帳單還欠很多沒交
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.54,1:18:44.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,it makes me nervous not to take no precaution.\N{\rCHT}若不避孕 我有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.78,1:18:50.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you don't want no more of my kids...\N{\rCHT}要是你不願給我生孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.72,1:18:53.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy to leave you alone.\N{\rCHT}我倒是樂意讓你落個清淨
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.02,1:18:58.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd have 'em, if you'd support 'em.\N{\rCHT}要是你能養活孩子 我就願意生
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.78,1:19:18.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Custody of the two minor chiIdren...\N{\rCHT}兩位年幼的孩子...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.68,1:19:20.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alma Del Mar Jr. and Jennifer Del Mar...\N{\rCHT}小阿爾瑪•德•瑪爾和珍妮芙•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.81,1:19:22.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,is awarded to plaintiff.\N{\rCHT}由原告撫養
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.81,1:19:25.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Defendant is ordered to pay child support to plaintiff...\N{\rCHT}法庭判決被告每月為每個孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.45,1:19:29.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the sum of $125 per month for each of the minor children...\N{\rCHT}向原告支付125美元撫養費
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.06,1:19:32.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,until they reach the age of 18 years.\N{\rCHT}直到她們年滿18歲
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.06,1:19:36.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Del Mar divorce granted, this sixth day of November, 1975.\N{\rCHT}德•瑪爾離婚生效  1975年11月6日
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.06,1:19:44.79,chs,,0,0,0,,\N{\fn華文楷體}歡迎到懷俄明
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.02,1:19:59.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,ln you go.\N{\rCHT}這邊走
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.26,1:20:12.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doin' here, huh?\N{\rCHT}你來這幹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.03,1:20:16.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got your message about the divorce.\N{\rCHT}收到你離婚的消息了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.87,1:20:18.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here.\N{\rCHT}過來
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.81,1:20:23.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, this here's Jack. Jack, these are my little girls.\N{\rCHT}這位是傑克 她們是我女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.61,1:20:26.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's Alma Jr. and Jenny. Hi.\N{\rCHT}這是小阿爾瑪和珍妮
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.21,1:20:28.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Say hi, girls.     - Hi.\N{\rCHT}- 打聲招呼 孩子們  - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.55,1:20:37.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got your card that the divorce came through.\N{\rCHT}我收到你的卡片 離婚辦好了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.72,1:20:40.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.     - So here I am.\N{\rCHT}- 嗯  - 所以我來了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.79,1:20:43.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I had to ask about 10 different people in Riverton...\N{\rCHT}為打聽你的地址
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.96,1:20:45.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,where you had moved to.\N{\rCHT}我在瑞弗頓都問了不下10個人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.90,1:20:53.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I guess, I thought that this means you....\N{\rCHT}我想 那意味著你…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.67,1:21:00.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, Jack, I don't know what to say.\N{\rCHT}不 傑克 我不知道該說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.95,1:21:05.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,See, I got the girls this weekend and....\N{\rCHT}瞧 這週末孩子們來了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.58,1:21:07.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jeez, l....\N{\rCHT}天啊 我…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.69,1:21:11.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sure as hell sorry. You know I am.\N{\rCHT}我很抱歉 你懂的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.02,1:21:16.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,See, I only get them once a month, and I missed last month.\N{\rCHT}瞧 一個月我只能見她們一次 上個月我都錯過了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.93,1:21:19.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I just.... Because of the roundup.\N{\rCHT}因為趕牧的事兒
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.37,1:21:22.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,So....\N{\rCHT}所以...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.67,1:21:27.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well....   - Yeah, all right.\N{\rCHT}- 那麼...  - 那好 算了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.41,1:21:30.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack.\N{\rCHT}傑克
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.51,1:21:34.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll see you next month, then.\N{\rCHT}那麼下個月再見吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.51,1:22:24.74,chs,,0,0,0,,\N{\fn華文楷體}距墨西哥邊境68英里
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.16,1:23:27.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Comin' up.\N{\rCHT}來咯
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.06,1:23:33.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here we go. Here we are!\N{\rCHT}菜來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.97,1:23:39.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, Rodeo.\N{\rCHT}等等 牛仔
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.27,1:23:42.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,The stud duck do the carvin' around here.\N{\rCHT}切肉讓給我來幹吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.37,1:23:45.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,You bet, LD. I was just saving you the trouble.\N{\rCHT}當然 我是想讓你省些麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.45,1:23:55.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bobby, if you don't eat your dinner...\N{\rCHT}波比 不安心吃飯
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.59,1:23:57.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to turn off that television.\N{\rCHT}我就把電視關掉
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.79,1:23:58.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why, Mama?\N{\rCHT}為什麼？媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.99,1:24:01.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be eating this food for the next two weeks.\N{\rCHT}接下來兩周都要吃這個
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.59,1:24:03.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, you heard your mama.\N{\rCHT}聽你媽的話
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.83,1:24:09.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,You finish your meal, and then you can watch the game.\N{\rCHT}把飯吃完才能看球賽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.25,1:24:22.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy?\N{\rCHT}爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.25,1:24:26.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy.\N{\rCHT}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.29,1:24:31.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hell, we don't eat with our eyes.\N{\rCHT}該死 吃飯又不用眼睛
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.19,1:24:33.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want your boy to grow up...\N{\rCHT}你也想你兒子長成一個…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.83,1:24:35.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,to be a man, don't you, Daughter?\N{\rCHT}男子漢 不是嗎？女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.79,1:24:38.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Boys should watch football.\N{\rCHT}男孩就該看足球
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.00,1:24:44.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not until he finishes eating the meal...\N{\rCHT}吃完他媽媽花3小時做好的飯
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.77,1:24:48.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,that his mama took three hours to fix.\N{\rCHT}才能看球賽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.28,1:25:02.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now you sit down, you old son of a bitch!\N{\rCHT}給我坐下 你這老雜種！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.66,1:25:07.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is my house, this is my child...\N{\rCHT}這是我家 他是我兒子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.36,1:25:09.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you are my guest. Now you sit down...\N{\rCHT}你是我客人 現在給我坐下...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.73,1:25:12.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,before I knock your ignorant ass into next week.\N{\rCHT}要不有的你好看
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.51,1:26:06.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy, tell about when you rode broncs in the rodeo.\N{\rCHT}爸爸 說說你參加競技牛仔比賽的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.19,1:26:11.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a short story, honey.\N{\rCHT}可沒啥好說的 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.62,1:26:14.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,lt was only about three seconds I was on that bronc.\N{\rCHT}我也只騎上去大約3秒種
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.86,1:26:19.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,The next thing I knew, I was flying through the air...\N{\rCHT}接下來 我就飛在天上了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.46,1:26:22.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,only I was no angel like you and Jenny here.\N{\rCHT}只是我並非你和珍妮那樣的天使
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.57,1:26:24.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,I didn't have no wings.\N{\rCHT}我沒有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.21,1:26:30.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that's the story of my saddle bronc career.\N{\rCHT}這就是我的競技牛仔生涯
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.60,1:26:55.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,There you go.\N{\rCHT}呐 給你
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.37,1:27:04.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,You ought to get married again, Ennis.\N{\rCHT}你該再找個伴結婚 埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.38,1:27:07.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Me and the girls worry about you bein' alone so much.\N{\rCHT}我和孩子們都擔心你太孤單了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.98,1:27:10.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, once burned....\N{\rCHT}可是 一朝被蛇咬....
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.92,1:27:17.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,You still go fishing with Jack Twist?\N{\rCHT}還和傑克•崔斯特去釣魚？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.96,1:27:21.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not often.\N{\rCHT}不常去了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.96,1:27:28.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, I used to wonder how come you never brought any trouts home.\N{\rCHT}知道嗎 我常納悶為什麼不見你帶鮭魚回來
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.43,1:27:30.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You always said you caught plenty...\N{\rCHT}你常說你釣到很多魚
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.10,1:27:32.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you know how me and the girls like fish.\N{\rCHT}你也知道我和孩子們喜歡吃魚的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.74,1:27:37.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, one night, I got your creel case open...\N{\rCHT}因此 有天晚上 在你去釣魚之前那晚
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.68,1:27:40.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,night before you went on one of your little trips.\N{\rCHT}我打開你的魚杆線軸
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.75,1:27:45.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Price tag still on it after five years.\N{\rCHT}都5年了 價簽還在上面
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.28,1:27:49.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I tied a note to the end of the line.\N{\rCHT}我在線頭上系個字條
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.76,1:27:54.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,lt said, "Hello, Ennis, bring some fish home. Love, Alma."\N{\rCHT}寫著"嗨 埃尼斯 帶些魚回來 愛你的阿爾瑪"
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.03,1:27:57.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then you come back lookin' all perky...\N{\rCHT}可你喜滋滋地回家
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.00,1:28:01.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,and said you caught a bunch of brownies and you ate them up.\N{\rCHT}說你釣到很多棕魚 都吃個精光
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.10,1:28:02.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?\N{\rCHT}你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.77,1:28:06.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I looked in that case first chance I got...\N{\rCHT}我馬上就去看了線軸
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.80,1:28:08.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there was my note still tied there.\N{\rCHT}我的字條還系在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.37,1:28:10.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,That line hadn't touched water in its life.\N{\rCHT}魚線壓根沒浸過水
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.21,1:28:12.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,That don't mean nothing, Alma.\N{\rCHT}阿爾瑪 那說明不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.24,1:28:14.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't try and fool me no more, Ennis.\N{\rCHT}別再騙我了 埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.61,1:28:17.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know what that means. Jack Twist.\N{\rCHT}我知道那說明了什麼 傑克•崔斯特
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.68,1:28:22.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Alma.    - Jack "Nasty"!\N{\rCHT}- 阿爾瑪  - 噁心的傑克！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.69,1:28:26.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You didn't go up there to fish. You and him...\N{\rCHT}你和他不是去釣魚 你是和他…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.09,1:28:29.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now you listen to me, you don't know nothing about it.\N{\rCHT}聽我說 你什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.09,1:28:30.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going to yell for Monroe.\N{\rCHT}我要喊門羅了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.80,1:28:32.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,You do it and I'll make you eat the fucking floor.\N{\rCHT}你敢喊 我就讓你啃地板
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.00,1:28:34.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get out!\N{\rCHT}滾！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.10,1:28:36.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you, too! Get out! Get out!\N{\rCHT}滾 滾！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.77,1:28:39.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get out of my house, Ennis Del Mar! You hear me? You get out!\N{\rCHT}滾出我的房子 埃尼斯•德•瑪爾！聽到沒？你給我滾
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.74,1:28:41.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy?\N{\rCHT}爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.84,1:28:43.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alma?\N{\rCHT}阿爾瑪？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.81,1:28:47.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bye, Daddy!\N{\rCHT}再見 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.98,1:28:50.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bye.\N{\rCHT}再見
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.06,1:29:06.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, asshole, watch where you're goin'!\N{\rCHT}嘿 白癡 走路看著點！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.93,1:29:09.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus. What....\N{\rCHT}天啊....
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.04,1:29:13.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus....\N{\rCHT}天啊....
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.80,1:29:15.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,You stupid fuck!\N{\rCHT}你這個雜種！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.81,1:29:21.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,God damn!\N{\rCHT}該死的！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.28,1:29:28.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,God. God damn.\N{\rCHT}該死的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.42,1:29:32.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\N{\rCHT}該死的！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.94,1:30:24.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,All I'm sayin' is, what's the point of making it?\N{\rCHT}我的意思就是 這有什麼意義呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.44,1:30:27.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,If the taxes don't get it, the inflation will eat it all up.\N{\rCHT}即便稅金免了 通脹還是把利潤吃個精光
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.25,1:30:36.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should see Lureen punchin' numbers in her adding machine.\N{\rCHT}你該瞧瞧洛琳用加法機算數的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.45,1:30:39.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hunting for extra zeros, her eyes gettin' smaller and smaller.\N{\rCHT}狠命找多幾個零出來 眼睛越盯越緊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.39,1:30:42.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's like watchin' a rabbit tryin' to...\N{\rCHT}就像土狼死追著
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.89,1:30:45.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,squeeze into a snake hole with a coyote on its tail.\N{\rCHT}鑽蛇洞逃生的兔子一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.83,1:30:48.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's some high class entertainment, if you ask me.\N{\rCHT}你這麼一說 倒確實有趣了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.33,1:30:52.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,For what it's worth.\N{\rCHT}值得一笑
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.34,1:30:59.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,You and Lureen, it's normal and all?\N{\rCHT}你和洛琳 你們還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.55,1:31:03.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sure.\N{\rCHT}當然
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.85,1:31:07.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,She don't ever suspect?\N{\rCHT}她從不起疑？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.13,1:31:20.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,You ever get the feelin'...\N{\rCHT}你可曾有種感覺
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.93,1:31:22.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know...\N{\rCHT}我說不上來
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.93,1:31:24.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,when you're in town...\N{\rCHT}當你在鎮子裡
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.47,1:31:27.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,and someone looks at you...\N{\rCHT}有人盯著你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.34,1:31:29.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,suspicious, like he knows.\N{\rCHT}疑神疑鬼地 好像他知道
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.14,1:31:33.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then you go out on the pavement and everyone's lookin' at you...\N{\rCHT}然後你走在路上 每個人都盯著你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.84,1:31:35.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,like they all know, too?\N{\rCHT}好像人人都知道一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.35,1:31:44.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you ought to get out of there, you know?\N{\rCHT}那麼 或許你就該離開那 知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.66,1:31:49.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Find yourself someplace different, maybe Texas.\N{\rCHT}去換個地方 比如德州
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.56,1:31:51.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Texas?\N{\rCHT}德州？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.70,1:31:55.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sure, and maybe you can convince Alma...\N{\rCHT}那好 或許你還可以說服阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.37,1:31:57.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,to let you and Lureen adopt the girls.\N{\rCHT}讓你和洛琳收養女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.47,1:31:59.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then we could just live together, herdin' sheep.\N{\rCHT}然後我們可以一起生活 牧羊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.97,1:32:02.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,And it'll rain money from L.D. Newsome...\N{\rCHT}洛琳她老子撒錢下來
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.51,1:32:05.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,and whiskey will flow in the streams. Jack, that's real smart.\N{\rCHT}還有喝不完的威士卡 傑克 那可真妙
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.28,1:32:06.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go to hell, Ennis Del Mar.\N{\rCHT}去死吧 埃尼斯•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.81,1:32:09.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanna live your miserable fucking life? Then go right ahead.\N{\rCHT}你想過這可憐的日子？ 那麼你去過吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.45,1:32:11.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fine. I was just thinkin' out loud.\N{\rCHT}好 我只是要想個辦法而已
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.45,1:32:14.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yup, you're a real thinker there. God damn....\N{\rCHT}嗯 你真是個思想家 媽的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.72,1:32:17.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack fucking Twist.\N{\rCHT}他媽的傑克•崔斯特
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.59,1:32:19.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got it all figured out, ain't he?\N{\rCHT}你都想到了？自以為是
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.20,1:32:25.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, hon.\N{\rCHT}好 甜心
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.98,1:32:42.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just finished my shift. Wanna dance?\N{\rCHT}我剛收工 來跳支舞？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.18,1:32:46.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I was on my way to the...    - I'm Cassie. Cassie Cartwright.\N{\rCHT}- 我要去…  - 我是凱西 凱西•卡特賴特
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.25,1:32:49.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis. Del Mar.\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.18,1:33:21.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,No more dancin' for me, I hope.\N{\rCHT}別再跳了 我希望
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.72,1:33:23.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You're safe.    - Yeah?\N{\rCHT}- 你放心吧  - 真的？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.32,1:33:26.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,- My feet hurt.    - Hard work, is it?\N{\rCHT}- 我腳疼  - 工作辛苦 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.36,1:33:30.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, drunks like you demanding beer after beer...\N{\rCHT}是的 招待你這樣的酒鬼 一杯接一杯
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.79,1:33:33.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,smokin'. Gets tiresome.\N{\rCHT}還不停抽煙 很疲憊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.60,1:33:37.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you do, Ennis Del Mar?\N{\rCHT}你是幹什麼的？埃尼斯•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.47,1:33:42.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, earlier today, I was castrating calves.\N{\rCHT}就今天 剛剛我還在替牛閹割
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.28,1:33:49.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你在幹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.51,1:33:51.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Trying to get a foot rub, dummy.\N{\rCHT}足底按摩 傻子
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.79,1:33:57.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}那好
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.79,1:34:00.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,That good?\N{\rCHT}感覺好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.48,1:34:24.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then I pledged Tri Delt at SMU.\N{\rCHT}接著我在南衛理公會大學加入了婦聯會
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.58,1:34:25.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I sure never thought...\N{\rCHT}我可真沒想到
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.95,1:34:28.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd end up in a poky little place like Childress.\N{\rCHT}我落在奇德瑞斯這個小地方
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.42,1:34:30.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then I met old Randall here at an Aggie game...\N{\rCHT}後來在農校遇到蘭德爾
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.79,1:34:33.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,and he was an animal husbandry major.\N{\rCHT}他是畜牧專業的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.46,1:34:35.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,So we've been here for a month and he got the foreman job...\N{\rCHT}我們在這一個月了 他找了份工頭的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.06,1:34:39.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,over at Roy Taylor's ranch. Like it or not, here I am!\N{\rCHT}在羅伊•泰勒的農場 不管怎樣 我來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.63,1:34:43.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Was you Tri Delt? I was Kappa Phi myself.\N{\rCHT}你是婦聯會的？我可是大學兄弟會的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.10,1:34:47.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, even though we ain't quite sorority sisters...\N{\rCHT}即使我們不是婦聯會姐妹...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.01,1:34:50.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,we just may have to dance with ourselves, Lureen.\N{\rCHT}可我們也只能自己跳舞了 洛琳
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.31,1:34:53.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our husbands ain't the least bit interested in dancin'.\N{\rCHT}我們的老公對跳舞一點興趣也沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.21,1:34:55.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,They ain't got a smidgen of rhythm between them.\N{\rCHT}他們一點節奏感也沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.41,1:34:56.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's funny, isn't it?\N{\rCHT}很滑稽 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.55,1:35:00.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Husbands don't never seem to wanna dance with their wives.\N{\rCHT}當老公的似乎都不願意和老婆跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.95,1:35:03.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is, Jack?\N{\rCHT}知道為什麼嗎？傑克
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.85,1:35:06.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I never give it any thought.\N{\rCHT}不知道 從未想過
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.22,1:35:08.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wanna dance?\N{\rCHT}跳支舞？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.03,1:35:12.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, thank you.     - Do you mind?\N{\rCHT}- 好啊 謝謝  - 不介意吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.56,1:35:15.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, it's all right. Go ahead.     - All right.\N{\rCHT}- 不 沒關係 跳吧  - 那好
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.47,1:35:17.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pardon us.\N{\rCHT}失陪了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.77,1:35:19.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking me to dance with you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你邀我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.64,1:35:21.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate that. Randall never does.\N{\rCHT}我很感激 蘭德爾從不請我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.87,1:35:23.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Last time I did, I think it was our wedding.\N{\rCHT}上回還是在婚禮上
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.74,1:35:26.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing you and Lureen happened along when you did...\N{\rCHT}你和洛琳正巧路過真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.18,1:35:28.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,or else we'd still be stuck on the side of the road...\N{\rCHT}要不我們只能困在路上
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.38,1:35:29.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,in that darn pickup.\N{\rCHT}那破舊貨車裡
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.71,1:35:31.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told Randall we ought to take the car.\N{\rCHT}我告訴過蘭德爾該買倆轎車
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.28,1:35:32.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course, he'd never listen to me.\N{\rCHT}當然 他從不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.88,1:35:35.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't listen to me if he was goin' deaf tomorrow.\N{\rCHT}即使明天變聾子了 他也不會聽我話的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.95,1:35:39.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told him it'd take more than chewing gum and baling wire...\N{\rCHT}我跟他講過 縫縫補補可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.09,1:35:40.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,to fix that pickup.\N{\rCHT}修不了那貨車的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.72,1:35:42.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, he's never been very mechanical, though.\N{\rCHT}他對機械也不是很熟
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.37,1:35:56.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You ever notice how a woman will powder her nose...\N{\rCHT}你注意到女人外出聚會前
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.57,1:35:58.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,before she goes to a party?\N{\rCHT}是如何塗脂抹粉的？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.58,1:36:02.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then she'll powder it again once the party's over.\N{\rCHT}接著聚會結束了 還要補妝一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.31,1:36:05.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, why powder your nose just to go home and go to bed?\N{\rCHT}我是說 回家上床怎麼還要塗脂抹粉的？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.88,1:36:07.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't know.\N{\rCHT}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.05,1:36:09.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Even if I wanted to know...\N{\rCHT}即便我想知道
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.49,1:36:12.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get a word in with Lashawn long enough to ask.\N{\rCHT}她一直在說 我也插不上話去問
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.82,1:36:16.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Woman talks a blue streak.     - Lively little gal.\N{\rCHT}- 女人就愛唧唧喳喳  - 可愛小女人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.10,1:36:26.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll like working for Roy Taylor.\N{\rCHT}為羅伊•泰勒工作 你會滿意的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.27,1:36:29.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- He's solid, Roy.   - Yeah, Roy. He's a good old boy.\N{\rCHT}- 他很踏實 羅伊  - 是呀 羅伊 人不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.88,1:36:37.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's got a little cabin down on Lake Kemp.\N{\rCHT}他在肯普湖有個小屋
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.05,1:36:41.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got a crappie house, little boat.\N{\rCHT}一間漁屋 一葉扁舟
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.99,1:36:44.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Said I could use it whenever I want.\N{\rCHT}他說我可以隨時用的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.26,1:36:50.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,We ought to go down there some weekend.\N{\rCHT}那天抽個週末我們去玩玩
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.73,1:36:54.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Drink a little whiskey, fish some.\N{\rCHT}喝喝酒 釣釣魚
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.57,1:36:57.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get away, you know?\N{\rCHT}放鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.04,1:37:02.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,That was right out of SMU.\N{\rCHT}就在離開南衛理公會大學之後
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.61,1:37:05.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,I could've had my pick of pretty much any job in North Dallas.\N{\rCHT}在北達拉斯 我差不多可選任何工作
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.14,1:37:07.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,So my pick was Neiman Marcus, which was a disaster...\N{\rCHT}我選了間高級百貨公司 真是場災難
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.58,1:37:10.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,because, honey, where clothes is concerned, I got no resistance.\N{\rCHT}因為 親愛的 只要是和衣服相關的 我就無法抗拒了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.75,1:37:14.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was spending more than I made. More than Randall ever will make.\N{\rCHT}我真的入不敷出 連蘭德爾的薪水也不夠
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.08,1:37:15.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,We come out here...\N{\rCHT}我們來到這
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.15,1:37:17.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,thinkin' that ranchin' was still big hats and Marlboros.\N{\rCHT}以為經營牧場還是 大蓋帽和萬寶路之類的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.32,1:37:19.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Boy, were we behind the times.\N{\rCHT}天啊 我們可是落伍了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.87,1:37:38.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Junior. You ready?\N{\rCHT}嗨 乖女兒 準備好了？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.32,1:37:55.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\N{\rCHT}你在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.89,1:37:59.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your daddy ever gonna see fit to settle down again?\N{\rCHT}你爸爸真能和我相處 並安定下來？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.53,1:38:03.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't know. Maybe he's not the marrying kind.\N{\rCHT}不知道 或許他不是那種該結婚的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.87,1:38:08.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't think so?\N{\rCHT}你真這麼想？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.27,1:38:11.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Or you don't think I'm the one for him?\N{\rCHT}還是你覺得我不適合他？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.68,1:38:16.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're good enough.\N{\rCHT}你挺好的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.49,1:38:24.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't say much, but you get your point across.\N{\rCHT}你話不多 可字字說到點子上了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.86,1:38:29.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't mean to be rude.\N{\rCHT}對不起 我不想無禮的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.10,1:38:33.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}好了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.03,1:38:36.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're stayin' on your feet, cowboy.\N{\rCHT}還不能讓你閑著 牛仔
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.67,1:38:39.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, darling.\N{\rCHT}失陪 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.06,1:39:05.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I'll pick you and Jenny up next weekend, after church.\N{\rCHT}下周禮拜過後 我來接你和珍妮
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.20,1:39:08.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fine.\N{\rCHT}好
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.97,1:39:13.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,You all right?\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.77,1:39:15.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}沒
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.04,1:39:18.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?\N{\rCHT}真的？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.78,1:39:24.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I was thinking, what with the new baby and all...\N{\rCHT}爸爸 我在想 又生了孩子後…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.02,1:39:27.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ma and Monroe have been awful strict on me.\N{\rCHT}媽媽和門羅對我更苛刻了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.48,1:39:29.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,More on me than Jenny even.\N{\rCHT}比對珍妮還要嚴
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.49,1:39:32.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was thinkin', maybe I could....\N{\rCHT}我想 或許我…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.99,1:39:37.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could come stay with you.\N{\rCHT}或許我可以搬來和你一起住
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.56,1:39:41.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd be an awful good help, I know I would.\N{\rCHT}我能幫你大忙的 我肯定
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.83,1:39:44.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, you know I ain't set up for that.\N{\rCHT}現在 我可不這麼想
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.67,1:39:48.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,With the roundup comin'...\N{\rCHT}馬上就要趕牧了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.47,1:39:51.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I won't ever be home.\N{\rCHT}我甚至都不在家
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.78,1:39:54.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Daddy.\N{\rCHT}那好吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.91,1:39:58.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm not sayin' that I wouldn't...    - It's all right, I understand.\N{\rCHT}- 我不是說我不想…  - 沒關係 我懂
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.25,1:40:03.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, see you on Sunday, then.\N{\rCHT}那 周日見
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.45,1:40:05.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bye.\N{\rCHT}再見
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.06,1:40:09.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bye, sweetheart.\N{\rCHT}再見 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.19,1:40:41.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Going to snow tonight for sure.\N{\rCHT}今晚肯定下雪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.73,1:40:43.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yup.\N{\rCHT}對
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.44,1:40:54.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,All this time and you ain't found nobody else to marry?\N{\rCHT}這麼久了 沒找一個稱心的結婚？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.71,1:40:58.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,I been puttin' the blocks...\N{\rCHT}我一直被瑞弗頓一漂亮女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.18,1:41:01.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,to a good-lookin' little gal over in Riverton.\N{\rCHT}牢牢栓著
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.55,1:41:06.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's a waitress. Wants to go to nursing school or somethin'.\N{\rCHT}她是個女招待 想讀衛校什麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.42,1:41:10.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\N{\rCHT}我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.29,1:41:16.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,What about you and Lureen?\N{\rCHT}你和洛琳呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.83,1:41:21.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lureen's good at making hard deals in the machinery business...\N{\rCHT}在生意上再怎樣也難不倒洛琳
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.70,1:41:24.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,but as far as our marriage goes...\N{\rCHT}可至於我們的婚姻
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.67,1:41:26.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,we could do it over the phone.\N{\rCHT}都是用電話維繫的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.81,1:41:39.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I kind of got this thing going with...\N{\rCHT}在瑞德斯 我差不多…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.45,1:41:43.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,a ranch foreman's wife over in Rutters.\N{\rCHT}和一個農場工頭的老婆好上了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.49,1:41:45.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What?     - I'm bound to get shot...\N{\rCHT}- 什麼？ - 每次偷偷去幽會
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.22,1:41:48.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,by Lureen or her husband each time I slip off to see her.\N{\rCHT}肯定要被洛琳或他丈夫射殺了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.73,1:41:51.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,You probably deserve it.\N{\rCHT}我看是你自找的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.70,1:42:00.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell you what.\N{\rCHT}告訴你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.31,1:42:06.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,The truth is...\N{\rCHT}其實真話是…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.82,1:42:17.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,sometimes I miss you so much, I can hardly stand it.\N{\rCHT}有時我真的很想你 想到我心痛
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.40,1:43:02.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll head up on to Lightning Flat.\N{\rCHT}我要回老家去一趟閃電平原
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.50,1:43:05.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,See the folks for a day or two.\N{\rCHT}去看父母一兩天
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.71,1:43:14.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's somethin' I been meanin' to tell you, bud.\N{\rCHT}有些話我要跟你說 老友
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.02,1:43:22.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it's likely November before I can come out here again.\N{\rCHT}我想要等到11月 我們才能再次見面了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.92,1:43:30.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,After we ship stock and before winter feedin' starts again.\N{\rCHT}等裝貨之後 冬季餵食之前
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.06,1:43:35.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,November.\N{\rCHT}11月
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.37,1:43:42.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,What in the hell ever happened to August?\N{\rCHT}那麼8月怎麼不行了？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.01,1:43:44.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well....\N{\rCHT}因為....
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.18,1:43:48.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Christ, Ennis.\N{\rCHT}該死的 埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.65,1:43:58.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, you had a fucking week to say some little word about this.\N{\rCHT}知道嗎 你有整周的時間來說這些
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.32,1:44:03.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why is it we're always in the friggin' cold?\N{\rCHT}為什麼我們總在這冰冷的地方見面？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.83,1:44:06.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,We ought to go south where it's warm, you know!\N{\rCHT}我們該去一些暖和的地方 知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.50,1:44:08.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,We ought to go to Mexico.\N{\rCHT}我們該去墨西哥
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.33,1:44:10.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mexico?\N{\rCHT}墨西哥？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.87,1:44:14.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hell, Jack, you know me. About all the travelin' I ever done...\N{\rCHT}該死 傑克 你知道我得 我所有的旅行...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.44,1:44:17.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,is around a coffee pot, looking for the handle.\N{\rCHT}就像在咖啡壺旁邊找把手
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.94,1:44:22.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, Jack. Lighten up on me.\N{\rCHT}別這樣 傑克 開心一點
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.38,1:44:26.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,We can hunt in November.\N{\rCHT}11月我們可以打獵
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.18,1:44:28.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Kill us a nice elk.\N{\rCHT}打只麋鹿
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.45,1:44:33.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll try if I can get Don Wroe's cabin again.\N{\rCHT}我再試試能不能弄到唐洛的小屋
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.39,1:44:36.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,We had a good time that year, didn't we?\N{\rCHT}那年我們過得很開心 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.73,1:44:41.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's never enough time, never enough.\N{\rCHT}開心的日子總是太短 太短
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.90,1:44:47.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, friend...\N{\rCHT}你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.74,1:44:52.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,this is a goddamn bitch of an unsatisfactory situation.\N{\rCHT}現在這樣子 我他媽的真是不爽
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.28,1:44:56.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You used to come away easy. Now it's like seein' the Pope.\N{\rCHT}從前你來去瀟灑 現在卻像朝拜教皇
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.88,1:45:01.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack, I got to work.\N{\rCHT}傑克 我得工作
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.75,1:45:07.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,ln them earlier days, I'd just quit the job.\N{\rCHT}要是以前 我就乾脆辭掉
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.39,1:45:11.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,You....\N{\rCHT}你....
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.40,1:45:15.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,You forget what it's like bein' broke all the time.\N{\rCHT}你忘了一直窮苦是什麼滋味
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.27,1:45:21.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You ever hear of child support?\N{\rCHT}聽說過子女撫養費嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.44,1:45:27.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you this, I can't quit this one...\N{\rCHT}我告訴你 這工我不能辭
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.84,1:45:29.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I can't get the time off.\N{\rCHT}我也不能翹班了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.78,1:45:35.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,lt was hard enough gettin' this time.\N{\rCHT}這次已經不容易了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.85,1:45:37.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,The trade-off was August.\N{\rCHT}交易在8月進行
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.73,1:45:43.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, you got a better idea?\N{\rCHT}那 你還有主意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.40,1:45:47.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I did, once.\N{\rCHT}曾經 我有過
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.00,1:45:51.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,You did, once.\N{\rCHT}曾經 你有過
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.34,1:45:58.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, have you been to Mexico, Jack Twist?\N{\rCHT}那麼 你去過墨西哥嗎？傑克•崔斯特
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.54,1:46:05.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,'Cause I hear what they got in Mexico for boys like you.\N{\rCHT}因為我聽說在墨西哥 有為你這樣的人服務
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.82,1:46:10.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hell, yes, I've been to Mexico. ls that a fucking problem?\N{\rCHT}該死 是 我去過墨西哥 你他媽的有意見？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.46,1:46:21.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell you this one time, Jack fucking Twist.\N{\rCHT}這次我老實告訴你 他媽的傑克•崔斯特
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.93,1:46:23.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I ain't foolin'.\N{\rCHT}我不是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.04,1:46:28.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,What I don't know, all them things that I don't know...\N{\rCHT}要是讓我知道了 那些我不知道的...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.11,1:46:32.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,could get you killed if I come to know them.\N{\rCHT}我不知道的事情 你就死定了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.18,1:46:37.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,I ain't jokin'.\N{\rCHT}我沒開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.52,1:46:45.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well try this one, and I'll say it just once.\N{\rCHT}那好 那就這樣 我也把話說出來
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.26,1:46:47.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Go ahead!     - I'll tell you what.\N{\rCHT}- 你說！ - 我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.02,1:46:49.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,We could have had a good life together.\N{\rCHT}我們本可以過上好日子
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.56,1:46:52.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fucking real good life. Had us a place of our own!\N{\rCHT}真正的好日子 有我們自己的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.80,1:46:55.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you didn't want it, Ennis.\N{\rCHT}可你不想這樣 埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.93,1:46:58.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,So what we got now is Brokeback Mountain!\N{\rCHT}所以我們只有這斷背山
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.97,1:47:04.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everything's built on that! That's all we got, boy. Fucking all.\N{\rCHT}就這斷背山 這就是我們的一切 他媽的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.34,1:47:06.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I hope you know that, if you don't never know the rest!\N{\rCHT}要是其他的你不明白 至少我希望你意識到這些
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.04,1:47:09.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,God damn it. You count the damn few times...\N{\rCHT}該死的 你自己數數
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.38,1:47:11.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,that we have been together in nearly 20 years...\N{\rCHT}20年來我們在一起才多少天
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.25,1:47:13.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you measure the short fucking leash you keep me on...\N{\rCHT}再想想你把我栓得有多苦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.45,1:47:16.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then you ask me about Mexico and you tell me you'll kill me...\N{\rCHT}最後你在質問我墨西哥的事情 並威脅要殺了我
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.15,1:47:19.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,for needin' somethin' I don't hardly never get!\N{\rCHT}就因為我想要一些 我從未得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.79,1:47:25.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how bad it gets!\N{\rCHT}你根本不知道這有多苦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.26,1:47:31.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I'm not you! I can't make it...\N{\rCHT}我不像你 一年可以只在…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.27,1:47:34.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,on a couple of high-altitude fucks once or twice a year!\N{\rCHT}這高山上幹一兩次！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.37,1:47:39.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,You are too much for me, Ennis.\N{\rCHT}我愛你愛到心痛 埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.38,1:47:42.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You son of a whoreson bitch!\N{\rCHT}你這該死的雜種
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.68,1:47:47.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew how to quit you!\N{\rCHT}多希望我知道如何放棄你
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.55,1:47:51.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you?\N{\rCHT}那你為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.22,1:47:56.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just let me be, huh?\N{\rCHT}為什麼不離開我 啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.73,1:48:01.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's because of you, Jack, that I'm like this.\N{\rCHT}都是因為你 傑克 我才落得這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.37,1:48:06.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm nothin'.\N{\rCHT}一無是處
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.44,1:48:08.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm nowhere.\N{\rCHT}無依無靠
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.51,1:48:16.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's okay.    - Get the fuck off me!\N{\rCHT}- 別這樣  - 放開我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.22,1:48:25.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's all right.\N{\rCHT}別這樣 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.89,1:48:28.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Ennis.\N{\rCHT}你這該死的 埃尼斯
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.83,1:48:32.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just can't stand this anymore, Jack.\N{\rCHT}我再也忍不下去了 傑克
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.94,1:48:46.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on now, you're sleepin' on your feet like a horse.\N{\rCHT}來 瞧你像馬兒一樣站著睡著了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.75,1:48:51.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,My mama used to say that to me when I was little.\N{\rCHT}小的時候 我媽常這麼對我說
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.95,1:48:54.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,And sing to me.\N{\rCHT}並對我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.50,1:49:09.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got to go.\N{\rCHT}我該走了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.84,1:49:14.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,See you in the morning.\N{\rCHT}回頭見
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.93,1:50:11.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\N{\rCHT}我走開一下
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.33,1:50:17.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey.\N{\rCHT}嗨
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.37,1:50:19.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis Del Mar.\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.44,1:50:24.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where you been?\N{\rCHT}最近忙什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.94,1:50:28.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here and there.\N{\rCHT}四處忙忙
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.15,1:50:34.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I left word for you with Steve at the ranch.\N{\rCHT}在農場 我讓斯蒂夫給你留了口信
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.18,1:50:38.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you must've got those notes I left at your place.\N{\rCHT}你一定收到我在你家留的字條了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.36,1:50:45.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Looks like I got the message, in any case.\N{\rCHT}不管怎樣 我算是收到字條了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.40,1:50:48.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Carl?\N{\rCHT}卡爾？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.33,1:50:52.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Carl's nice.\N{\rCHT}是 卡爾人不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.07,1:50:54.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,He even talks.\N{\rCHT}至少他說說話
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.77,1:50:59.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good for you.\N{\rCHT}那你滿意了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.61,1:51:02.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}對
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.72,1:51:07.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good for me.\N{\rCHT}我很滿意
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.56,1:51:15.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't get you, Ennis Del Mar.\N{\rCHT}我不懂你 埃尼斯•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.20,1:51:22.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.01,1:51:33.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was probably no fun anyways, was l?\N{\rCHT}我可能很無趣 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.01,1:51:39.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis, girls don't fall in love with fun.\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯 女人戀愛不是為了找趣
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.69,1:52:16.75,chs,,0,0,0,,\N{\fn華文楷體}"傑克 11月我們見面好嗎？"\N收件人已故
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.69,1:52:26.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hello.    - Hello, this is Ennis DeI Mar.\N{\rCHT}- 喂  - 喂 我是埃尼斯•德•瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.67,1:52:31.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who? Who is this?\N{\rCHT}哪位？你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.87,1:52:35.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ennis Del Mar. I'm an old buddy of Jack's.\N{\rCHT}埃尼斯•德•瑪爾 我是傑克的老友
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.77,1:52:38.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack used to mention you.\N{\rCHT}傑克曾提起過你
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.24,1:52:42.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're the fishing buddy or the hunting buddy, I know that.\N{\rCHT}你是和他打獵、釣魚的好友 我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.01,1:52:45.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would have let you know what happened...\N{\rCHT}本該告訴你發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.85,1:52:48.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I wasn't sure about your name or address.\N{\rCHT}可我不清楚你的名字和地址
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.45,1:52:51.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack kept his friends' addresses in his head.\N{\rCHT}傑克把朋友的地址記在腦海裡
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.29,1:52:56.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm callin', to see what happened.\N{\rCHT}我打電話是想問問 到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.23,1:52:59.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.\N{\rCHT}哦 對
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.20,1:53:05.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack was pumpin' up a flat on the truck...\N{\rCHT}在回家的路上爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.23,1:53:07.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,out on a back road, when the tire blew up.\N{\rCHT}傑克給輪胎打氣
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.10,1:53:11.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,The rim of the tire slammed into his face...\N{\rCHT}輪胎圈砸在面門上
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.21,1:53:15.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,broke his nose and jaw and knocked him unconscious on his back.\N{\rCHT}砸斷了他的鼻子和下巴 他不省人事
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.38,1:53:19.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,By the time somebody come aIong, he'd drowned in his own bIood.\N{\rCHT}等到有人發現 他已經失血過多死去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.95,1:53:22.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,He was onIy 39 years oId.\N{\rCHT}才39歲
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.56,1:53:29.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?\N{\rCHT}喂？喂？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.23,1:53:32.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N{\rCHT}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.10,1:53:38.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Was he buried down there?\N{\rCHT}已經下葬了？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.84,1:53:40.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,We put a stone up.\N{\rCHT}給他立了墓碑
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.74,1:53:42.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,He was cremated, like he wanted.\N{\rCHT}如他所願 我們安排火葬
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.84,1:53:47.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Half his ashes was interred here, the rest was sent up with his folks.\N{\rCHT}一半骨灰安葬在這裡 另一半送給他的父母
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.38,1:53:52.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,He use to say he wanted his ashes scattered on Brokeback Mountain...\N{\rCHT}他曾說過希望把骨灰撒在斷背山
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.48,1:53:54.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I wasn't sure where that was.\N{\rCHT}可我不知道在哪
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.25,1:53:59.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought Brokeback Mountain might be around where he grew up.\N{\rCHT}我以為斷背山就是他長大的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.09,1:54:00.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Knowing Jack...\N{\rCHT}以為那是傑克...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.46,1:54:02.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,it might be some pretend place...\N{\rCHT}假想的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.79,1:54:05.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,where bluebirds sing and there's a whiskey spring.\N{\rCHT}鳥兒歌唱 美酒流淌
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.97,1:54:10.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, ma'am...\N{\rCHT}不 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.47,1:54:14.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,we was herdin' sheep on Brokeback one summer...\N{\rCHT}63年的夏天 我和他曾在斷背山上
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.24,1:54:16.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,back in '63.\N{\rCHT}一起牧羊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.08,1:54:28.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, he said it was his favorite place.\N{\rCHT}那麼 他說過那是他最鐘意的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.15,1:54:33.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought he meant to get drunk. He drank a lot.\N{\rCHT}我以為他喝醉了 他酗酒很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.56,1:54:39.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is his folks still up in Lightning Flat?\N{\rCHT}他的父母還住在閃電平原嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.10,1:54:42.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,They'll be there till the day they die.\N{\rCHT}他們會一直住在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.84,1:54:49.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.67,1:54:52.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I sure am sorry.\N{\rCHT}我真的很難過
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.51,1:54:55.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,We was good friends.\N{\rCHT}我們是很好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.45,1:55:04.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get in touch with his folks.\N{\rCHT}去看看他父母吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.75,1:55:08.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I suppose they'd appreciate it if his wishes was carried out.\N{\rCHT}如果他的願望實現 我相信他父母會感激你的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.39,1:55:12.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,About the ashes, I mean.\N{\rCHT}我是指骨灰
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.16,1:56:16.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Want a cup of coffee, don't you? Piece of cherry cake?\N{\rCHT}喝杯咖啡？櫻桃餅？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.66,1:56:18.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am, I'll have a cup of coffee...\N{\rCHT}謝謝 夫人 我喝杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.29,1:56:21.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I can't eat no cake just now. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}不用櫻桃餅了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.14,1:56:32.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I feel awful bad about Jack.\N{\rCHT}傑克的事情我很難過
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.14,1:56:36.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.45,1:56:41.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't begin to tell you how bad I feel.\N{\rCHT}再怎樣說也表達不了我的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.25,1:56:46.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,I knew him a long time.\N{\rCHT}我與他相識多年
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.06,1:56:51.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,I come by to say that...\N{\rCHT}我來是想說
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.69,1:56:55.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,if you want me to take his ashes up there on Brokeback...\N{\rCHT}他太太說他希望 骨灰被撒在斷背山上
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.07,1:56:58.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,like his wife said he wanted to...\N{\rCHT}如果你們需要我去
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.27,1:57:01.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,then I'll be happy to.\N{\rCHT}那麼我很願意
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.17,1:57:05.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what.\N{\rCHT}我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.98,1:57:09.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know where Brokeback Mountain is.\N{\rCHT}我知道斷背山在哪
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.65,1:57:14.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thought he was too goddamn special to be buried in the family plot.\N{\rCHT}我曾想他太他媽的特殊 而不該葬在墓園
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.19,1:57:19.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack used to say....\N{\rCHT}傑克曾經提起
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.76,1:57:23.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Ennis Del Mar," he used to say.\N{\rCHT}"埃尼斯•德•瑪爾" 他經常說到
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.09,1:57:28.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,"I'm gonna bring him up here one of these days...\N{\rCHT}"總有一天我要帶他來這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.00,1:57:31.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,"and we'll lick this damn ranch into shape."\N{\rCHT}然後我和他一起把這破爛農場搞好"
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.37,1:57:35.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,He had some half-baked notion...\N{\rCHT}他有些大致的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.27,1:57:37.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,the two of you was gonna move up here...\N{\rCHT}你們倆搬到這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.34,1:57:39.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,build a cabin...\N{\rCHT}蓋間小屋
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.98,1:57:42.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,help run the place.\N{\rCHT}一起經營這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.28,1:57:48.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then, this spring...\N{\rCHT}可是 今年春天
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.62,1:57:52.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,he got another fella gonna come up here with him...\N{\rCHT}他和另一個人來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.52,1:57:58.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,build the place, help run the ranch.\N{\rCHT}蓋了房子 經營農場
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.73,1:58:03.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Some ranch neighbor of his from down in Texas.\N{\rCHT}好像是他在德州的農場鄰居
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.23,1:58:08.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gonna split up with his wife and come back here...\N{\rCHT}他說要和老婆分居
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.34,1:58:10.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,so he says.\N{\rCHT}並搬到這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.54,1:58:14.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,But, like most of Jack's ideas...\N{\rCHT}可 這和傑克很多想法一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.71,1:58:18.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,never come to pass.\N{\rCHT}都沒能實現
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.58,1:58:25.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,I kept his room like it was when he was a boy.\N{\rCHT}他的房間我一直留著 還和他小時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.86,1:58:28.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think he appreciated that.\N{\rCHT}我覺得他喜歡那樣
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.53,1:58:36.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,You are welcome to go up to his room, if you want.\N{\rCHT}若你願意 歡迎上去坐坐
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.41,1:58:44.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd like that. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}嗯 我去看看 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.89,2:01:47.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell you what.\N{\rCHT}我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.99,2:01:53.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,We got a family plot. He's goin' in it.\N{\rCHT}家裡有墓園 他得葬在那裡
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.40,2:01:57.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}是 先生
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.27,2:02:02.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You come back and see us again.\N{\rCHT}下次再來看看我們
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.89,2:02:18.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你 夫人
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.18,2:03:18.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey there, Junior.    - Hey, Daddy.\N{\rCHT}- 你好 乖女兒  - 嗨 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.69,2:03:28.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here.\N{\rCHT}來啊
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.79,2:03:33.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like the car?\N{\rCHT}喜歡這車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.73,2:03:36.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. Is it yours?     - It's Kurt's.\N{\rCHT}- 喜歡 你的車？  - 科特的
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.27,2:03:40.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I thought you were seein' Troy.     - Troy?\N{\rCHT}- 我以為你和特洛伊交朋友呢  - 特洛伊？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.94,2:03:43.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy, that was two years ago.\N{\rCHT}老爸 那是兩年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.61,2:03:46.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Troy still playing baseball?\N{\rCHT}特洛伊還在打藍球？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.28,2:03:50.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's doing. I'm seein' Kurt now.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 我在和科特約會
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.88,2:03:54.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, what does Kurt do?     - Works out in the oil fields.\N{\rCHT}- 科特是幹嗎的？  - 在油田工作
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.82,2:03:59.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So he's a roughneck, huh?     - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 那麼他是莽漢啦 啊？  - 是呀
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.99,2:04:03.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I guess you're 19, you can do whatever you want. lsn't that right?\N{\rCHT}你都19了吧？ 自己的事情自己作主吧
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.89,2:04:05.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sure.\N{\rCHT}當然
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.80,2:04:16.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Daddy, you need more furniture.    - Yeah, well...\N{\rCHT}- 爸爸 你需要添些傢俱  - 可是...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.51,2:04:20.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,if you got nothin', you don't need nothin'.\N{\rCHT}要是一無所有 那也落個清淨
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.61,2:04:26.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, what's the occasion?\N{\rCHT}那麼 有何喜事？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.02,2:04:32.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Me and Kurt...\N{\rCHT}我和科特
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.82,2:04:35.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,we're getting married.\N{\rCHT}我們要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.46,2:04:39.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well....\N{\rCHT}那麼
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.66,2:04:43.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,So how long have you known this guy for?\N{\rCHT}你認識那傢伙多久？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.37,2:04:44.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,About a year.\N{\rCHT}大約一年
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.84,2:04:50.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our wedding will be June 5, at the Methodist church.\N{\rCHT}婚禮在6月5號 衛理公會教堂
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.51,2:04:54.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny will be singing and Monroe is gonna cater the reception.\N{\rCHT}珍妮會唱歌 門羅將負責接待
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.78,2:05:02.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now this Kurt fella...\N{\rCHT}那麼科特那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.12,2:05:06.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,he loves you?\N{\rCHT}他愛你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.36,2:05:10.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Daddy.\N{\rCHT}是的 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.23,2:05:13.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,He loves me.\N{\rCHT}他愛我
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.67,2:05:23.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Was hopin' you'd be there.\N{\rCHT}希望你能來
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.48,2:05:27.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}好
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.88,2:05:35.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think I'm supposed to be on a roundup down near the Tetons.\N{\rCHT}我想那時我可能要去提頓附近趕牧
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.31,2:05:57.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what?\N{\rCHT}你猜這麼著？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.24,2:06:02.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I reckon they can find themselves a new cowboy.\N{\rCHT}我想他們可以另找一個牛仔
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.11,2:06:07.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,My little girl, getting married.\N{\rCHT}我的乖女兒要出嫁了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.26,2:06:23.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,To Alma and Kurt.\N{\rCHT}敬阿爾瑪和科特
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.81,2:07:45.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jack, I swear....\N{\rCHT}傑克 我發誓....

